>>># <Patient Management>

#   >> Required Fields:
        > Name, Age, Sex, Contact Number, Address
        > Bloodtype, Allergies, Medical History, Current Medications
        > Priority Type (0 = Normal, 1 = Emergency) - for Queuing/sechduling
        > Active or Inactive 
#   >> Optional Field:
        > Bool for allowing Deletion of patient record/account
        > Bool to track status fields of Patient


>>>#  <Doctor Management >

    Required Fields:
        > Name, Sex, Specialty, Contact Number, Address
        > Availability/Work Schedule 
            Sunday To Monday 
            - Pwede sa monday na 7am - 12pm tas sa tuesday pang hapon. 
            - Pwede din na di available yung doctor ng isang araw.
        
>>># <Appointment Scheduling>  

* Create appointment in FIFO within same date time slot
* Provide an option for a normal or priority.
* Validate patient exists; 
* Reject time conflicts.

        Mag set tayo ng mga limits kada schedule appointments.
        For example si doc avail siya from 7am to 12pm, kada appointment pwede tumagal ng 1hr - so sa loob ng sched niya na 7-12, 5 lang pwede niya i handle.
        Tas need din na if may naka puno na yung schedule ni doc. if Normal lang naman yung queue, pwede mag suggest ng ibang date&time slot or kung ano mas maganda para i handle yung case pag may mga ganon.

#   >> Required Fields: 
        > Multiple Normal & Priority Queues (isa kada doctor, naka depende sa priority level).
            Pili nalang siguro if mag normal queue or priority queue

        > Queue Number (Number ng Patient sa Pila nung queue)
            ket nag increment nalang yung number (ex. 1001,1002,1003, and so on.)
    
#   >> Functions (Method sa Class):  

        Dequeue(Serve/Attend): 
            Serve the earliest scheduled appointment. Aalisin na yung sa unahan ng queue, bale parang okay na siya treated na.
            Papalitan na rin yung field nung patient na status dun sa patient record na class.
            Mas okay siguro if pag na serve na status maging
            Dadagdag to sa Treatment History Record ni Patient.
            
        View Queues/Scheduled Appointments: Queue number must be displayed and can be viewed both by patient and doctor.

        Cancel: Remove a SCHEDULED appointment by appointment.

        Reschedule: Let the patient update date/times lot of their appointment.
